<p>
  Once you have uploaded some attachments you will be able to see their
  names along with a <code>Download</code> button on the right. Pressing
  on the button will cause that attachment to be downloaded.
</p>

<h4 class="subsection-title">Deleting</h4>

<p>
  Just as in the case of modules there are two ways to delete a
  lesson. You can press on the red cross on the right of a lesson's name
  or you can press on the <code>Delete</code> button on the bottom of
  a lesson edit page.
</p>

